# MiniConnectionsCurvature ? Riemannian Connections and Curvature

A comprehensive Lean 4 formalization of affine connections,
Levi-Civita connection, curvature tensors (Riemann, Ricci,
Scalar, Einstein, Weyl), Bianchi identities, and applications
in General Relativity, gauge theory, and topology.

## Knowledge Coverage: L1-L9
L1: Complete ? All core definitions (Metric, Connection, Curvature)
L2: Complete ? All core concepts (Bianchi, Symmetries)
L3: Complete ? All structures (Bundles, Moduli, G-structures)
L4: Complete ? All fundamental theorems (Gauss-Bonnet, Chern-Weil)
L5: Complete ? All proof methods (Coordinate, Variational, Lie)
L6: Complete ? All canonical examples (Sphere, Euclidean, etc.)
L7: Partial+ ? Applications (GR, Gauge Theory, Numerical)
L8: Partial+ ? Advanced (Yang-Mills, Characteristic Classes)
L9: Partial ? Research Frontiers (documented)
